{"tid":1113001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：百萬人登記偷窺明星色情活動醜聞，顯示的不是香港人八卦，而是人格低賤。","createTime":"2019-04-17T17:04:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T07:23:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":93,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee5f15cf47c27738eab4b11f57ca8fa4ab4610c","tid":1113001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"陳雲：百萬人登記偷窺明星色情活動醜聞，顯示的不是香港人八卦，而是人格低賤。他們到底是香港人曾經喜愛過的明星，都是好努力鍛煉唱歌技藝和推銷自己的努力派，比起天王巨星，他們算是卑微，但他們是香港演藝行業的success stories，而香港人這樣對待他們。<br />\n<br />\n在我成長的七八十年代，明星濕水露點、不帶乳罩、俯身露出這些現象，當時的記者是不會拍攝或報導的，有時電影出來二十幾年之後，觀眾才看到以前的大明星是這樣信任觀眾的，因為當時的觀眾的下意識是看不到的。他們不看這些東西的。（以前曾經有個出身model的大明星在片場赤裸換衣服，場記嚇了一跳，但也沒有什麼聲張。）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集體起哄去偷窺曾經喜愛的明星，是背叛、是落井下石，是低賤人格。為了去偷窺而排除障礙去登記做用戶，更加是人格卑鄙。<br />\n<br />\n香港不必做什麼政治，因為超過一百萬人的媒體活躍人口是人格低賤的。這點共產黨要放下心頭大石了。這一百萬人，正正就是每年去六四悼念和參加〇三七一大遊行的泛民支持者。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n共產黨更加放心的是，這群人讀了陳雲這個評論，更加會憎恨陳雲，故此香港本土政治運動是沒有看頭的了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157036640822225?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157036640822225%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=hObUr7UKzm7jHRUyz9oMSK3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=40668303\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157036640822225?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\nWan Chin<br />\n香港人的真面目。大家看清楚。<br />\n<br />\nAlfred Law<br />\nWan Chin 老師好，憎你的人愈多，識得跟的走得愈易<br />\n<br />\nWan Chin<br />\nAlfred Law 是。邏輯學的排斥法，令人更加容易找到真理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHubert So<br />\n個時陳冠A 己經係咁"},{"pid":"9b4d78caabf5491cececfba9678d5d0b4e18188f","tid":1113001,"uid":25468,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:08:34.000Z","msg":"幾時先滅寂 ?"},{"pid":"6a03e9ffb875ae16b70c56b610b2852f60c4f920","tid":1113001,"uid":131691,"like":93,"dislike":6,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"陳雲完全miss咗個point<br />\n今次點解咁多人起哄係因為個明星本身holier than thou嘅態度令人神憎鬼厭<br />\n大家唔係「低賤人格」，而係「正常人睇一個虛偽嘅賤人扮聖人露出馬腳而集體恥笑」"},{"pid":"3b22e79055a5191ca2c2e491952c757b57583242","tid":1113001,"uid":96965,"like":68,"dislike":7,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"每次有d驚人小小既事發生<br />\n成班戇尻衝撚哂出黎講長篇大論<br />\n以為好撚好似好有偉論咁<br />\n講到自己好高尚咁<br />\n話發生乜乜事就見到全香港點點點<br />\n講到咁撚巴柒閉<br />\n又唔睇下自己個撚樣點樣撚法"},{"pid":"a5f41e8d4477cda613a2cf84171aab0053d76485","tid":1113001,"uid":37757,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:16:00.000Z","msg":"集體起哄去偷窺曾經喜愛的明星，是背叛、是落井下石，是低賤人格。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d242e133b0384bc16fc74d687e868e91d27ef0d6","tid":1113001,"uid":35919,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"sor 從來冇喜愛過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7367fe34d46c46e4de6cd2df18df564fdbe6f521","tid":1113001,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:25:13.000Z","msg":"集體起哄去反對曾經喜愛的老師，是背叛、是落井下石，是低賤人格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4d346b5c239402e3eda89ddf1c3ee9d9a936d4","tid":1113001,"uid":26910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d0b19f20f8a496a4e867ee5f11ee6a0ab96f8f0","tid":1113001,"uid":49197,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:30:39.000Z","msg":"許志安都仲可圈可點，黃心穎有咩值得觀眾喜愛？又柒又矮又冇料"},{"pid":"f3d9b94eda8991d349c48dd5bcd64b8069827bc0","tid":1113001,"uid":26910,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:31:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24634aff9cd4ffc92a45af1b8da97206d0e77a0e","tid":1113001,"uid":94819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:32:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"96dbedc4064d36c1c83eeef3ea02854709008f38","tid":1113001,"uid":42283,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"你叫雞又品格高尚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b36331135624b281b2c71a98126753c09837abd","tid":1113001,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"7367fe34d46c46e4de6cd2df18df564fdbe6f521","tid":1113001,"uid":191926,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:25:13.000Z","msg":"集體起哄去反對曾經喜愛的老師，是背叛、是落井下石，是低賤人格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:54:42.000Z","msg":"輸咗咁耐都仲記住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c879b285af2cac7bd50774688e3efe61ea57ad9f","tid":1113001,"uid":156511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:57:06.000Z","msg":"d姑娘又比佢玩電腦？"},{"pid":"e6da983c067318680a1fd5a8e41165505fa1b22d","tid":1113001,"uid":247905,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:58:48.000Z","msg":"國師又中"},{"pid":"2b75a1a9fb59b2716da819664c0b8065cb137153","tid":1113001,"uid":61022,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:02:02.000Z","msg":"講到底蘋果同陳雲都係拿呢件事拿hit rate!<br />\n唔覺陳雲有乜咁高尚<br />\n<br />\n又話80年代無記者會登？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gSDqkC6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgSDqkC6.png&h=f4005993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用80年代同而家比有乜意義？<br />\n照佢咁講出軌係無野，反而睇下娛樂新聞就下賤？呢d係咩雙重標準？<br />\n<br />\n廢文"},{"pid":"1ff8b0e9a7d484e52380523a4bc63df9f029526e","tid":1113001,"uid":61022,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:09:46.000Z","msg":"陳雲自己有無睇過？<br />\n如果無睇有乜資格論？<br />\n如果有咁陳雲是否「底賤」其中一人"},{"pid":"88b5cad7d8862be0a972ce6140c5859bde0ccdf1","tid":1113001,"uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"On9 用佢邏輯全世界冇乜人唔賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dccba0ede3ba936d250655fd580b00bb4d0d39","tid":1113001,"uid":2748,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"陳雲：老香港，一種莫名的悲哀感。昨日在街上行路去理髮店，一路聞到的都是四川雲南辣麵辣米線的刺鼻氣味，蠻夷山番的氣味。以前在上水、元朗或深水埗街頭聞到的雲吞湯的淡淡蝦殼魚湯味已經消失。<br />\n雲吞麵以前是粗食，上不得廳堂，但屬於粗食細做。銀絲細麵，在滾湯之中散開燙熟，散尾小雲吞，全部要即做即食，漉麵的廚房不能距離顧客太遠，就在店門之側。以前的店家甚至計算了麵檔距離顧客的步數，雲吞麵下面要放匙羹隔起麵，以免雲吞麵放久了而變得軟糊不爽。<br />\n這些源自廣州羊城的精工烹調，九七之後二十年，就在香港消失。<br />\n建立維艱，淪落好容易。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢篇寫得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169dac2bd1f1a55e61fc7c0b80619f2c41d26ae5","tid":1113001,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:16:01.000Z","msg":"中!!"},{"pid":"14f4a69f7ab9622dd519264c7c2288d795a72984","tid":1113001,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:19:26.000Z","msg":"老師又中"},{"pid":"f6241c3130c7414807013c992c3291886042de23","tid":1113001,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fd82bce9abc860a8fb44c63ebd76671eb15bd0","tid":1113001,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:02:16.000Z","msg":"你自己咪一樣叫雞"},{"pid":"bd1c3c07637d5e9354df3eecde04206f3dac5d8d","tid":1113001,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:02:21.000Z","msg":"陳雲第一日落香港？<br />\n<br />\n國師自己都叫鷄啦"},{"pid":"f57f3a375789490f585e0f379ab958b736fc6b6d","tid":1113001,"uid":135169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"#城邦之夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陳雲直頭下流添啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}